backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613904\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jhf1665703068168.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jhf1665703068168.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jhf1665703068168.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jhf1665703068168\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines whether the picture widget is vertically expanded when it is printed. <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> (default).\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jhf1665703068168__p_d101876e1_d101877e1_d101878e1\">\n         \n                                AllowVerticalExpansion\n                                <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jhf1665703068168__table_d11996e1_d11997e1_d11998e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jhf1665703068168__table_d11996e1_d11997e1_d11998e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jhf1665703068168__table_d11996e1_d11997e1_d11998e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jhf1665703068168__table_d11996e1_d11997e1_d11998e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jhf1665703068168__table_d11996e1_d11997e1_d11998e1__entry__2\">Expand the picture widget to fit the image, so\n                     that the complete image can be printed.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jhf1665703068168__table_d11996e1_d11997e1_d11998e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jhf1665703068168__table_d11996e1_d11997e1_d11998e1__entry__2\">The picture widget maintains its size and the\n                     image is sized inside the existing picture widget area.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jhf1665703068168__section_uz4_kwl_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d481777e128\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jhf1665703068168__p_d101882e1_d101883e1_d101884e1\">This property affects printing only if\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Preserve Aspect Ratio</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>. In this case,\n            allows vertical expansion of the picture widget when it is printed, by the amount\n            required to preserve the image's aspect ratio.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jhf1665703068168__p_d101885e1_d101886e1_d101887e1\">To set this property for all picture widgets, add\n            it to the picture widget's definition in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jhf1665703068168__section_cqw_lwl_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d481777e149\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jhf1665703068168__pre_d24_nwl_vwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(PIC) = \"AllowVerticalExpansion=True\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jhf1665703068168__section_mjr_nwl_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d481777e158\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxc1665703126500.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxc1665703126500.html\" title=\"The upicture widget is used to displays the contents of an Image field. Uniface provides a logical widget called Picture, which is mapped to upicture.\">upicture (Picture)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yxe1665702611833.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect)</a><p>Determines whether the aspect ratio of the image is preserved at all times. True (default) or False.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613904\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613904\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Allow Vertical Expansion (AllowVerticalExpansion) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 This property determines whether the picture widget is vertically expanded when it is printed. True or False (default). AllowVerticalExpansion = \" True | False \" Value Description True Expand the picture widget to fit the image, so that the complete image can be printed. False The picture widget maintains its size and the image is sized inside the existing picture widget area. Description This property affects printing only if Preserve Aspect Ratio is True . In this case, allows vertical expansion of the picture widget when it is printed, by the amount required to preserve the image's aspect ratio. To set this property for all picture widgets, add it to the picture widget's definition in the .ini file. Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(PIC) = \"AllowVerticalExpansion=True\" Copy Applies To upicture (Picture) Related Links Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect) Determines whether the aspect ratio of the image is preserved at all times. True (default) or False. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}